              <p><img src='static/images/doc/1521090176024.png' alt='1521090176024' /></p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>我们可以在日历的账户信息中选择显示哪个账户的日历</p>
              <p><img src='static/images/doc/1521090550697.png' alt='1521090550697' /></p>
              <p>&nbsp;</p>
            </li>
          </ol>
